						               													<description>A card game inspired by a detective drama of the Showa era.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player becomes one of the &amp;quot;five unique detectives&amp;quot; and investigates the case by allocating 24 hours each. Five cases are set at the same time, and a five-row, plot-type auction is held.&amp;nbsp;Scores will be given to the 1st and 2nd place &amp;quot;in the time allotted&amp;quot; for each case. Do this for 3 hands.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Detectives work together to investigate the case, but often go to stand, play to seek credit, or settle with the culprit.&amp;nbsp;As a result, you may get deeply involved in the incident and get seriously injured or you may be killed!&amp;#227;&amp;#128;&amp;#128;Moreover, even if you get a line of duty, the game is not over, and if you can get a line of duty at a good show, you can earn a high score.&amp;nbsp;Produce your own line of duty scene well and decide &amp;quot;What's this !!!!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The basis of the game is a &amp;quot;5-row, plot-type auction&amp;quot;.&amp;#227;&amp;#128;&amp;#128;A total of 24 common cards will be given to the player as a hand, and one card will be placed in each of the five cases, for a total of five cards.&amp;nbsp;After placing, reveal the cards, and after seeing the result, arrange the remaining 5 sheets in the same way and judge by the total value.&amp;nbsp;Therefore, it is important to avoid competition as much as possible and get more cases efficiently, because it is possible to guess to some extent who wants which case with the first placement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then, shouldn't it be better to hide the information by arranging as few numbers as possible for the first placement?&amp;nbsp;Of course, that's one strategy.&amp;nbsp;However, if the numbers are the same, there is a rule that the one with the larger number placed on the first sheet wins, so it is not always advantageous to arrange the smaller numbers.&amp;#227;&amp;#128;&amp;#128;In addition, each person has a ticket called hero time, and you can win regardless of the number unless the heroes spend time fighting with each other.&amp;nbsp;Where to use this hero time is also important.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
